title: Concord, Pemiscot County, Missouri
text:
Concord is an <a href="unincorporated%20community">unincorporated community</a> in <a href="Pemiscot%20County%2C%20Missouri">Pemiscot County</a>, in the <a href="U.S.%20state">U.S. state</a> of <a href="Missouri">Missouri</a>.
History.
The community once contained a church and a school, which both are now defunct. The area derives its name from the Concord Baptist Church, founded in 1898.
